1 Infrastructure (firewall/router/switches/APs)

10 Services (homelab stuff, outbound via proxy only)

20 Trusted (PCs/Tablets/Phones, allow out to any)

30 Untrusted (Guest wifi etc, allow out to internet, block to other VLANs)

40 IoT (trusted smart devices that need internet access, allow out to internet, Home Assistant, and NAS)

50 NoT (isolated smart devices like CCTV cams, allow out to HA and NAS only, no internet)

70 Trusted devices connected remotely via Wireguard (allow out to any)

99 Outbound VPN (primarily for sailing the high seas or evading geoblocking, allow out to internal VLANs and internet routed via VPN gateway, block out to WAN gateway)